ICE_CHP file:
		system_type:		Type of system that indicates the plant configuration.
		max-capacity:		This item is not used by now.
		pump_on:		A flag that indicates if the pump of radiator is ON or OFF
		storagetank_size:	Size of the storage tank is defined by the hours of IC engine operations that required to charge the tank
					completely.
		HWtank_siz:		Size of the hot water tank is defined by the hours of IC engine operations that required to charge the hot
					water tank completely.